          "id": "b3a424787e4b_2",
          "href": null,
          "name": "8f0f",
          "text": "Our Carbon Footprint is a significant part of our more general Ecological Footprint. We have already mentioned this measure before. Our ecological footprint can be defined as “the impact of human activities measured in terms of the area of biologically productive land and water required to produce the goods consumed and to assimilate the wastes generated” (WWF, 2015).",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
          "hasDropCap": null,
          "dropCapImage": null,
          "iframe": null,
          "layout": null,
          "markups": [
            {
