              "href": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ecological_footprint",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 63,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            },
            {
              "end": 368,
              "href": "http://wwf.panda.org/about_our_earth/teacher_resources/webfieldtrips/ecological_balance/eco_footprint/",
              "rel": "",
              "start": 359,
              "title": "",
              "anchorType": "LINK",
              "linkMetadata": null,
              "type": "A",
              "name": null,
              "creatorIds": null
            }
          ],
          "type": "P"
        },
        {
          "id": "b3a424787e4b_3",
          "href": null,
          "name": "d04e",
          "text": "The graphs below show how much of the increase in humanity’s ecological footprint is due to an increase in our carbon footprint since the 1960s; the second graph also illustrates the other contributions to our ecological footprint besides carbon.",
          "metadata": null,
          "mixtapeMetadata": null,
